Summary : This image displays the logo and company name of "CÔNG TY TNHH ICETEA SOFTWARE", featuring both Vietnamese and English text along with a geometric symbol.

logo:  
Company Name & Tagline :  
  • Vietnamese: "CÔNG TY TNHH ICETEA SOFTWARE" (translates to "ICETEA SOFTWARE Co., Ltd.").  
  • English: "Icetea Software" (with "Icetea" in grey and "Software" in bold black).

Symbol & Design :  
  • Central geometric symbol: red, composed of interlocking lines forming a stylised, symmetrical square with two small red squares at opposite corners.  
  • The symbol is placed above the English company name.

Layout & Placement :  
  • Vietnamese company name is centered at the top in large, bold serif font.  
  • Geometric logo is centered below the company name.  
  • English company name is centered below the logo, with "Icetea" in grey and "Software" in bold black sans-serif font.

Analysis :  
  • The logo uses a red geometric motif to convey a modern, tech-oriented brand identity.  
  • The dual-language presentation suggests a company operating in both Vietnamese and international contexts.  
  • The bold, clean design and central alignment reinforce a professional and contemporary image. <!-- figure, from page 0 (l=0.243,t=0.042,r=0.703,b=0.310), with ID 685416d3-7bcb-43e3-a256-c19fb6132dc3 -->
